  "description": "The Ubiquiti U7 Outdoor Access Point is designed for use in the challenging weather conditions, delivering exceptional connectivity. This weatherproof solution features advanced Wi-Fi 7 technology that delivers blazing fast speeds, ultra-low latency, and exceptional ability to handle multiple devices simultaneously. The access point offers exceptional throughput rates, reaching up to 5.012 Gbps across 2.4 GHz and 5 GHz bands, making it ideal for demanding outdoor applications. Whether you need seamless Wi-Fi coverage for your patio, pool area, or outdoor workspace, the U7 Outdoor provides a reliable and scalable solution.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Weatherproof Wi-Fi 7 Solution",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti U7 Outdoor Access Point is designed for use in the challenging weather conditions, delivering exceptional connectivity. This weatherproof solution features advanced Wi-Fi 7 technology that delivers blazing fast speeds, ultra-low latency, and exceptional ability to handle multiple devices simultaneously. The access point offers exceptional throughput rates, reaching up to 5.012 Gbps across 2.4 GHz and 5 GHz bands, making it ideal for demanding outdoor applications. Whether you need seamless Wi-Fi coverage for your patio, pool area, or outdoor workspace, the U7 Outdoor provides a reliable and scalable solution."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Powerful Performance",
      "text": "The U7 Outdoor boasts impressive technical specifications for tackling outdoor Wi-Fi challenges. It features 4 spatial streams for efficient data transmission, smooth streaming, lag-free video conferencing, and reliable connectivity for over 200 connected devices. The access point comes equipped with a unique combination of antennas: a high-gain directional internal antenna for focused long-range coverage and two external omni antennas. This innovative design allows you to leverage the directional antenna for extending coverage in a specific direction, or utilize the omni antennas with software-adjustable beamwidth for achieving balanced coverage in open spaces."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Effortless Installation",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti U7 Outdoor is built to withstand the elements. Its weatherproof (IPX6) enclosure protects it from dust, moisture, and extreme temperatures. The access point offers versatile mounting options for wall or pole installations, allowing for flexible placement within your outdoor space. Powered using PoE+, the U7 Outdoor eliminates the need for separate power supplies and simplifies installation. With its user-friendly design, future-proof Wi-Fi 7 technology, and powerful performance, the Ubiquiti U7 Outdoor is the ideal solution for extending reliable Wi-Fi connectivity to any outdoor environment."
    }
  ],
